traction. </step> <step id="-fea4g1_22"> Payment Process: <list id="-fea4g1_32"> <li id="-fea4g1_33">Select the bank from which you want to make the payment.</li> <li id="-fea4g1_34">Complete the payment process.</li> </list> </step> <step id="-fea4g1_23"> Finalize the Purchase: <list id="-fea4g1_35"> <li id="-fea4g1_36">You can choose to print the purchase order, view it, or simply submit it.</li> </list> </step> </procedure> </chapter>
